tionsThis paper introduces a two level video datarepresentation model in order to guide video data storage on a tertiary storage subsystemA simulation model hasbeen developed to evaluate dierent video placement strategies based on both Constructive and Iterative ImprovementapproachesExperimentation has been carried out for theproposed placement approaches as well as for a typical random placement policy which serves as a comparison refer enceIterative Improvement placement has been proven tooutperform the other considered video data placement approaches in both seek and service times.&lt;/p&gt;
